Dialogue: 0,00:01:22.54,00:01:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>They are an army unlike any other...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:01:25.17,00:01:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>crusading across the stars \Ntoward a place called UnderVerse,</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:01:29.09,00:01:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>their promised land...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:01:31.09,00:01:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>a constellation of dark new worlds.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:01:34.47,00:01:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Necromongers, they're called.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:01:36.97,00:01:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>And if they cannot convert you, \Nthey will kill you.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:01:42.94,00:01:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Leading them, the Lord Marshal.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:01:46.06,00:01:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>He alone has made a pilgrimage \Nto the gates of the UnderVerse...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:01:50.19,00:01:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>and returned a different being.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:01:53.53,00:01:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Stronger. Stranger.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:01:56.87,00:02:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Half alive and half...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:02:00.20,00:02:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>something else.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:02:46.33,00:02:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Linin' him up for you. Port-side \Nshot comin' up. Steady. Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:57.97,00:03:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Steady.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:00.85,00:03:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Take it. Take it!</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:03:03.93,00:03:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the shot!
Dialogue: 0,00:03:08.48,00:03:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! \NToombs, we're runnin' out of road!
Dialogue: 0,00:03:11.19,00:03:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I got it! Again!
Dialogue: 0,00:03:15.94,00:03:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,00:03:18.78,00:03:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Toombs!
Dialogue: 0,00:03:35.13,00:03:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Riddick.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:50.35,00:03:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Three meters clearance port-side. \NOne and a half meters starboard.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:03:54.82,00:03:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We got a choke point comin' up.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:09.83,00:04:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>What the shit was that?</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:04:14.17,00:04:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Tags, you got eyes on Riddick?
Dialogue: 0,00:04:17.38,00:04:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Tags?
Dialogue: 0,00:04:23.76,00:04:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:26.35,00:04:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He just ghosted two guys, \Nand I never even saw him.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:30.94,00:04:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Toombs? \NI mean, maybe we oughta just...
Dialogue: 0,00:04:33.40,00:04:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're my new gunner.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:35.11,00:04:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Grab a Gat.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:44.45,00:04:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay on top of him this time.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:14.40,00:05:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>You made three mistakes.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:05:19.57,00:05:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,First, you took the job.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:23.20,00:05:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Second, you came light.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:25.28,00:05:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>A four-man crew for me? \NFuckin' insulting.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:05:29.95,00:05:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>But the worst mistake you made...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:05:34.96,00:05:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Empty gun rack.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:05:41.92,00:05:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's the bounty on my head? \N- One mil.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:47.60,00:05:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- One-point-five. \N- What slam pays 1.5 for a convict?
Dialogue: 0,00:05:52.31,00:05:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Private party.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:54.64,00:05:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey, hey! \NGuy, guy! Easy! Anonymous.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:57.65,00:06:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's what the sheet said. \N- What planet?
Dialogue: 0,00:06:02.40,00:06:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Helion Prime.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:11.62,00:06:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa. Where you going'? \NLast question.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:14.62,00:06:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And you better get this one right, merc.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:18.38,00:06:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose ship is this?
Dialogue: 0,00:06:22.21,00:06:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine?
Dialogue: 0,00:06:22.88,00:06:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong Answer
Dialogue: 0,00:06:43.53,00:06:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Knew they'd come for me.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:06:46.07,00:06:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Took 'em five years, but I knew.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:06:49.16,00:06:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>You don't expect these mercs \Nto have any honor, any code.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:06:55.58,00:06:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>But this new bounty from a holy man,</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:07:00.04,00:07:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>a guy whose neck I saved...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:07:04.46,00:07:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Well, lesson learned.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:07:06.47,00:07:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>No such word as "friend. "</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:07:09.26,00:07:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>It can only end bad \Nwhen you let someone get too close.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:07:13.72,00:07:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Bad for them.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:07:15.89,00:07:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>So now it's back to civilization</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:07:19.94,00:07:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,<i> all the brightness... \Nand everything I hate.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:07:24.94,00:07:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wanted to be left alone
Dialogue: 0,00:07:27.86,00:07:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Helion Prime is on alert condition four.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:07:35.70,00:07:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Unrecognized craft. You need to follow me \Nto Spaceport Six for security inspections.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:07:41.33,00:07:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Hey! Do you hear me?</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:07:44.63,00:07:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Follow me to Spaceport Six now!</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:08:36.85,00:08:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Imam, pray for us.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:39.77,00:08:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>It was confirmed \Ntwo seasons back. Yes.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:08:43.10,00:08:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>They're coming here. \NI mean, are we next?</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:08:45.52,00:08:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Militants storm...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:08:47.57,00:08:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Yes. But going to the underground \Nshelters if it happens...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:08:50.78,00:08:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>You're right. \NThat's what I thought too.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:08:53.03,00:08:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Are you staying or leaving?</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:08:55.58,00:08:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>It's the end of everything. \NEverything!</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:08:57.99,00:09:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Well, my neighbours... \NHalf my street is gone.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:09:01.54,00:09:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do? \NI don't know. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:03.54,00:09:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Hood of the devil. \NThat's what someone called 'em.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:09:05.54,00:09:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Them? Who is them? \NSome kind of new creature...
Dialogue: 0,00:09:07.71,00:09:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is nonsense. \NIt's all nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:09.76,00:09:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>So tall that it touches the clouds.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:09:13.72,00:09:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's nothing around this \Nstatue, this colossus. Nothing left.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:18.18,00:09:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's their calling card.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:30.90,00:09:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Did you know all your doors were locked?</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:09:39.16,00:09:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Five years ago,</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:09:41.58,00:09:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>I took two people off that planet...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:09:44.58,00:09:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>A kid, Jack, \Nwho everyone else thought was a boy,</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:09:48.88,00:09:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>and a holy man...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:09:51.63,00:09:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>searching for New Mecca.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:09:56.43,00:10:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>I told one man...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:10:01.27,00:10:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,where I might go.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:04.48,00:10:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I showed trust to one man.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:08.48,00:10:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I make a mistake, Imam?
Dialogue: 0,00:10:12.07,00:10:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no simple answer.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:14.49,00:10:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever was said \Nwas meant to give us a chance...
Dialogue: 0,00:10:19.24,00:10:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,a fighting chance.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:21.83,00:10:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Were it not for the threat of invasion, \NI never would have betrayed you.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:26.75,00:10:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So now who do I have to kill \Nto get this payday off my head?
Dialogue: 0,00:10:46.77,00:10:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>It is said the comet \Nalways precedes them...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:10:51.40,00:10:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,these world-enders.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:55.95,00:10:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The Coalsack planets are gone.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:57.95,00:11:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Eight million settlers missing.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:11:00.87,00:11:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>The entire Aquilan System is gone too.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:11:04.58,00:11:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Helion Prime shares its sunlight \Nwith all worlds nearby.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:11.09,00:11:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If we fall, they fall.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:15.88,00:11:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And after that...
Dialogue: 0,00:11:18.26,00:11:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My God, \Nhow do I save my family?
Dialogue: 0,00:11:25.81,00:11:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Have you heard anything I've said?</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:11:30.94,00:11:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it's all circling the \Ndrain... the whole universe.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:34.61,00:11:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>- Right? \N- That's right.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:11:45.58,00:11:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Had to end sometime.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:05.31,00:12:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The one you want is now here.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:25.29,00:12:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And whose throat is this?
Dialogue: 0,00:12:28.71,00:12:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you cut my throat, I'll not be able to \Nrescind the offer that brought you here.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:33.46,00:12:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nor tell you why it's so vital \Nthat you did come.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:36.05,00:12:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The blade comes off \Nwhen the bounty comes off.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:39.01,00:12:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Aereon, \Nan envoy from the Elemental race.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:42.72,00:12:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She means you no harm.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:49.02,00:12:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There are very few of us who have met \Na Necromonger and lived to speak of it.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:52.94,00:12:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Necromonger.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:54.86,00:13:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the name that will convert \Nor kill every last human life...
Dialogue: 0,00:13:00.45,00:13:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>There is a story, Riddick, \Nof young male Furyans...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:13:01.40,00:13:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>There is a story, Riddick, \Nof young male Furyans...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:13:03.07,00:13:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>There is a story, Riddick, \Nof young male Furyans...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:13:05.16,00:13:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,strangled at birth...
Dialogue: 0,00:13:07.74,00:13:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,strangled with their own cords.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:11.62,00:13:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,When Aereon told this story \Nto the Helion leaders,
Dialogue: 0,00:13:14.38,00:13:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I told her of you.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:16.54,00:13:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- What do you know of your early years? \N- Do you remember your home world?
Dialogue: 0,00:13:19.71,00:13:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where it was? \N- Have you met any others?
Dialogue: 0,00:13:22.26,00:13:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Others like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:26.89,00:13:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister, they don't know \Nwhat to do with just one of me.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:31.02,00:13:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Open up in there!</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:13:33.56,00:13:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>- Stand back! \N- Open up!</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:13:35.19,00:13:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I will send them away. \NBut wait one minute, please.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:38.69,00:13:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Will you wait one minute \Nto save worlds?</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:13:44.49,00:13:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Not my fight.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:47.28,00:13:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you will leave us \Nto our fate,
Dialogue: 0,00:13:49.62,00:13:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>just like you did her.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:13:52.04,00:13:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Break it down!</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:13:57.04,00:13:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:58.17,00:14:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Come. Let us try to send them away.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:03.97,00:14:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Move it. Come on. \NLeave us alone!</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:14:08.47,00:14:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no one here!
Dialogue: 0,00:14:11.93,00:14:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>You don't understand. \NHe can help us! He can help us!</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:14:18.94,00:14:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Go!</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:14:26.28,00:14:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not afraid of the dark, are you?
Dialogue: 0,00:14:49.64,00:14:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>- Get him! \N- Where is he?</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:14:52.27,00:14:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In there!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:21.54,00:15:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You mentioned her.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:24.13,00:15:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She, uh...
Dialogue: 0,00:15:27.05,00:15:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She went looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:29.05,00:15:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,People died. \NShe went to prison.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:32.56,00:15:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I don't remember where.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:37.39,00:15:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was a world so hot \Nyou could not survive on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:42.90,00:15:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- Crematoria. \N- Young Jack.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:46.44,00:15:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She thought of you \Nas her older brother.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:48.74,00:15:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- She worshipped you. \N- You were supposed to watch her.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:52.91,00:15:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>She never forgave you...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:15:55.62,00:15:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,for leaving just when \Nshe needed you most.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:59.08,00:16:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She needed to stay away \Nfrom me.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:03.71,00:16:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You all do
Dialogue: 0,00:16:14.22,00:16:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Furyans. \NDefiant to the end.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:54.89,00:16:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:57.81,00:17:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We go to the shelter.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:00.39,00:17:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We take only ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:24.00,00:17:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay close.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:58.49,00:18:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>No!</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:19:12.23,00:19:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Flight leaders, get all squads \Noff the ground now.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:19:14.94,00:19:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>We have heavy inbound.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:19:18.87,00:19:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Follow me in!</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:19:39.22,00:19:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The next shelter. \NThis way!
Dialogue: 0,00:19:41.47,00:19:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,00:19:43.56,00:19:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Whoo-hoo!</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:20:06.08,00:20:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see if it's safe.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:15.42,00:20:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- Stay back! \N- Come, Ziza.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:36.78,00:20:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,00:21:35.50,00:21:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Lajjun and Ziza!
Dialogue: 0,00:21:37.67,00:21:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- When it's over. \N- Let me go. I must get to my family!
Dialogue: 0,00:21:40.42,00:21:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's over.
Dialogue: 0,00:22:10.70,00:22:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Aah!
Dialogue: 0,00:22:42.23,00:22:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,In here.
Dialogue: 0,00:22:45.40,00:22:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in.
Dialogue: 0,00:22:49.45,00:22:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh.
Dialogue: 0,00:23:55.85,00:23:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>- Imam! \N- Don't follow me.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:25:33.16,00:25:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be \Nan afterlife for me.
Dialogue: 0,00:25:37.66,00:25:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Will there be for you?
Dialogue: 0,00:26:57.53,00:27:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go replenish the ranks.
Dialogue: 0,00:27:35.36,00:27:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,In this 'verse,
Dialogue: 0,00:27:38.70,00:27:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,life is antagonistic \Nto the natural state.
Dialogue: 0,00:27:44.33,00:27:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Here, humans in all \Ntheir various races...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:27:49.46,00:27:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,are a spontaneous outbreak...
Dialogue: 0,00:27:52.67,00:27:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,an unguided mistake.
Dialogue: 0,00:27:54.92,00:27:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Our purpose...
Dialogue: 0,00:27:57.01,00:28:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is to correct that mistake.
Dialogue: 0,00:28:02.01,00:28:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there is another 'verse...
Dialogue: 0,00:28:05.39,00:28:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,a 'verse where life \Nis welcomed and cherished.
Dialogue: 0,00:28:10.48,00:28:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>A ravishing, ever-new place \Ncalled UnderVerse.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:28:17.53,00:28:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>So it is this 'verse \Nthat must be cleansed of life,</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:28:23.20,00:28:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,so that UnderVerse \Ncan populate and prosper.
Dialogue: 0,00:28:30.04,00:28:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Look around you. \NEvery Necromonger in this hall,</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:28:34.67,00:28:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,every one of the Legion Vast that just \Nswept aside your defenses in one night...
Dialogue: 0,00:28:39.22,00:28:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,was once like you.
Dialogue: 0,00:28:42.01,00:28:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Fought as feebly as you.
Dialogue: 0,00:28:45.85,00:28:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Every Necromonger \Nthat lives today...
Dialogue: 0,00:28:48.85,00:28:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is a convert.
Dialogue: 0,00:28:51.02,00:28:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- There'll be no conversions! \N- We all began as something else!
Dialogue: 0,00:28:58.53,00:29:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It was hard for me to accept, too, \Nwhen I first heard these words.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:03.03,00:29:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But I changed.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:05.70,00:29:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I let them take away my pain.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:08.08,00:29:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- You betrayed your faith! \N- Just as you will change...
Dialogue: 0,00:29:12.37,00:29:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>when you realize that the threshold \Nto the UnderVerse will be crossed...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:29:17.88,00:29:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>only by those who have \Nembraced the Necromonger faith.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:29:21.26,00:29:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,For those of you \Nwho will right now...
Dialogue: 0,00:29:25.35,00:29:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,drop to your knees \Nand ask to be purified.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:29.48,00:29:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- We will not renounce our faith! \N- No one here will do what you ask.
Dialogue: 0,00:29:34.44,00:29:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It is unthinkable!
Dialogue: 0,00:29:35.94,00:29:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>This is a world of many peoples, \Nmany religions!</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:29:41.40,00:29:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And we simply cannot \Nand will not be converted!
Dialogue: 0,00:29:45.87,00:29:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll take your soul.
Dialogue: 0,00:30:00.01,00:30:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Join him...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:30:02.63,00:30:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Or join me.
Dialogue: 0,00:30:25.78,00:30:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your one chance.
Dialogue: 0,00:30:28.49,00:30:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the Lord Marshal's offer \Nand bow.
Dialogue: 0,00:30:31.04,00:30:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I bow to no man.
Dialogue: 0,00:30:41.05,00:30:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not a man.
Dialogue: 0,00:30:43.13,00:30:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the holy Half-Dead \Nwho has seen the UnderVerse.
Dialogue: 0,00:30:46.89,00:30:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I'm not \Nwith everyone here.
Dialogue: 0,00:30:49.47,00:30:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But I will take a piece of him.
Dialogue: 0,00:30:58.65,00:31:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A piece you will have.
Dialogue: 0,00:31:28.64,00:31:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Stop him!</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:31:43.07,00:31:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Irgun. One of my best.
Dialogue: 0,00:31:45.57,00:31:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so.
Dialogue: 0,00:31:51.74,00:31:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think of this blade?
Dialogue: 0,00:32:03.75,00:32:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's a half-gram heavy \Non the back end.
Dialogue: 0,00:32:06.21,00:32:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In our faith,
Dialogue: 0,00:32:08.22,00:32:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,you keep what you kill.
Dialogue: 0,00:32:17.68,00:32:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you familiar to me?
Dialogue: 0,00:32:22.56,00:32:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Have we met \Non some distant field?
Dialogue: 0,00:32:27.24,00:32:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd think I'd remember.
Dialogue: 0,00:32:30.53,00:32:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd think I would too.
Dialogue: 0,00:32:33.87,00:32:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him before the Quasi-Deads.
Dialogue: 0,00:33:20.75,00:33:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful eyes.
Dialogue: 0,00:33:23.13,00:33:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,00:33:27.88,00:33:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The last six Lord Marshals \Nhave called this home.
Dialogue: 0,00:33:32.05,00:33:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnificent, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,00:33:34.39,00:33:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- I might have gone a different way. \N- True of us all.
Dialogue: 0,00:33:40.14,00:33:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Converts receiving the mark \Nof the Necromonger.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:33:46.48,00:33:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They learn how one pain \Ncan lessen another.
Dialogue: 0,00:34:03.87,00:34:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There now.
Dialogue: 0,00:34:07.54,00:34:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That is just... perfect.
Dialogue: 0,00:34:14.22,00:34:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The more you resist them,
Dialogue: 0,00:34:17.51,00:34:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the greater the damage will be.
Dialogue: 0,00:34:22.43,00:34:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>A new one.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:34:25.52,00:34:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>You've brought us a new one.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:34:41.87,00:34:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting breeder.
Dialogue: 0,00:35:00.68,00:35:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Making entry.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:35:05.94,00:35:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>We've entered his neocortex.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:35:08.90,00:35:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>- Ahh! The Riddick! \N- Regress.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:35:12.82,00:35:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Scanning fresh memories.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:35:16.53,00:35:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Thoughts of someone called Jack.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:35:19.62,00:35:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Riddick!
Dialogue: 0,00:35:23.54,00:35:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Now we find thoughts of an Elemental.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:35:26.46,00:35:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>The one race that would slow \Nthe spread of Necromongers.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:35:29.71,00:35:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>- Furyans. \N- Furyans.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:35:37.30,00:35:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does he come from?
Dialogue: 0,00:35:39.55,00:35:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are his people? \NThese are the things I need to know.
Dialogue: 0,00:35:46.02,00:35:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>We find energy.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:35:50.44,00:35:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>We find Furyan energy.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:35:55.44,00:35:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>-He's Furyan!</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:35:57.99,00:36:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Furyan!</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:36:01.78,00:36:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>A Furyan survivor!</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:36:04.95,00:36:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Kill the Furyan! Kill the Riddick!</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:36:07.83,00:36:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Kill the Riddick! Kill the Riddick! \NKill the Riddick!</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:36:12.25,00:36:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill the Riddick.
Dialogue: 0,00:36:47.20,00:36:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Find him. Whatever it takes. Find him!
Dialogue: 0,00:37:24.99,00:37:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me guess. \NA five-man crew this time.
Dialogue: 0,00:37:30.08,00:37:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Couple of things \Nyou could have done better.
Dialogue: 0,00:37:36.71,00:37:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,First, trash the locator beacon \Ninside my ship... the one you jacked.
Dialogue: 0,00:37:41.42,00:37:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>And second... and this is really \Nthe more important part...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:37:44.84,00:37:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,dust my dick \Nwhen you get the chance.
Dialogue: 0,00:37:48.14,00:37:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- Any questions? \N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,00:37:54.44,00:37:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What took you so long?
Dialogue: 0,00:38:21.01,00:38:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Decoy launched.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:38:23.26,00:38:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In and out, unsuspected and undetected. \NDamn, I love a good smash-and-grab.
Dialogue: 0,00:38:27.47,00:38:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast. Not so fast.
Dialogue: 0,00:38:28.93,00:38:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>- Preparing to engage ion drive. \N- So,</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:38:31.93,00:38:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,where do we drop \Nyour merc-killin' ass?
Dialogue: 0,00:38:35.94,00:38:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Who's gonna pay \Nthe most for you now?</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:38:38.32,00:38:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- Butcher Bay? \N- Butcher Bay.
Dialogue: 0,00:38:42.11,00:38:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten minutes every other day \Non the dog run.
Dialogue: 0,00:38:44.95,00:38:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Protein waffles aren't bad.
Dialogue: 0,00:38:47.99,00:38:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how 'bout Ursa Luna? \NNice little double-max prison.
Dialogue: 0,00:38:51.95,00:38:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They keep a cell open for me... \Njust in case I drop in.
Dialogue: 0,00:38:56.42,00:38:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>You know the problem \Nwith these joints now?</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:38:58.42,00:39:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Health clubs \Nfor waffle-eatin' pussies.
Dialogue: 0,00:39:01.46,00:39:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should think about \Nuppin' our game here a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,00:39:04.26,00:39:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about someplace \Ntruly diabolical.
Dialogue: 0,00:39:06.68,00:39:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is he thinkin' now?
Dialogue: 0,00:39:08.76,00:39:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>He's thinkin' a triple-max prison.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:39:11.35,00:39:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>A no-daylight slam. \NOnly three of 'em left in this system...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:39:14.81,00:39:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,two of 'em outta range for a shitty little \Nunder cutter like this one with no legs.
Dialogue: 0,00:39:19.19,00:39:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Leavin' just... one...
Dialogue: 0,00:39:22.82,00:39:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Crematoria.
Dialogue: 0,00:39:25.78,00:39:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what you had in mind, \Nright, Toombs?
Dialogue: 0,00:39:28.66,00:39:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how does he know where we're goin', \Nand we don't?
Dialogue: 0,00:39:31.62,00:39:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Dope it out.
Dialogue: 0,00:39:32.37,00:39:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate this run.
Dialogue: 0,00:39:33.79,00:39:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,00:39:35.87,00:39:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know about this \Nnew crew of yours.
Dialogue: 0,00:39:37.96,00:39:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They seem a bit skittish.
Dialogue: 0,00:39:40.38,00:39:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably shouldn't tell 'em \Nwhat happened to the last crew.
Dialogue: 0,00:39:52.60,00:39:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you supposed \Nto be some slick-shit killer.
Dialogue: 0,00:39:57.19,00:39:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now look at you...
Dialogue: 0,00:39:59.77,00:40:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,all back-of-the-bus \Nand shit.
Dialogue: 0,00:40:39.52,00:40:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>I say we attack Helion Two next.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:40:42.23,00:40:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it straight \Ninto their teeth.
Dialogue: 0,00:40:44.23,00:40:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll cost you 20,000 heads, five \Nwarrior ships. Nothing more, I swear it.
Dialogue: 0,00:40:47.74,00:40:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,While I do prize brute force,
Dialogue: 0,00:40:51.11,00:40:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,this approach \Nis perhaps more artful.
Dialogue: 0,00:40:54.33,00:40:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Start at the end.
Dialogue: 0,00:40:57.25,00:40:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Go straight to Helion Five,
Dialogue: 0,00:40:59.29,00:41:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the last planet \Nin the system.
Dialogue: 0,00:41:01.58,00:41:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We approach from the night side.
Dialogue: 0,00:41:04.25,00:41:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Remove these cannon first,</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:41:07.30,00:41:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,then attack \Nthe larger placements at speed.
Dialogue: 0,00:41:10.22,00:41:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>We'll catch them on their rear flank. \NAnd in ten days' time,</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:41:13.09,00:41:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>the rest of those worlds \Nwill tumble before us.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:41:17.47,00:41:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, as with most, \Ntheir blind spot...
Dialogue: 0,00:41:19.89,00:41:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,is right behind them.
Dialogue: 0,00:41:24.27,00:41:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've located an ion trail \Nwhich leads off-world.
Dialogue: 0,00:41:27.90,00:41:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you should be \Noff-world, Vaako.
Dialogue: 0,00:41:30.65,00:41:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've deployed a tracker team. \NOne of the best.
Dialogue: 0,00:41:33.32,00:41:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wherever Riddick has gone, \Nyou lens him out and cleanse him.
Dialogue: 0,00:41:38.04,00:41:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,00:41:38.79,00:41:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to take a \Nfrigate for one breeder?
Dialogue: 0,00:41:42.12,00:41:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't question it, Vaako!
Dialogue: 0,00:41:46.09,00:41:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it on faith.
Dialogue: 0,00:41:52.01,00:41:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Mercenaries, Elementals, \NNecromongers...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:41:57.35,00:42:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Shit, I've never been so popular.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:42:01.35,00:42:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Should probably slip these chains \Nand open up a few arteries.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:42:06.40,00:42:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>But why drive, \Nwhen you can get driven?</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:42:09.61,00:42:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>A free ticket to Crematoria. \NThanks, Toombs.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:42:14.28,00:42:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Got me some business there \Nnamed Jack.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:42:18.28,00:42:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>And once we settle up, \NI'll walk away forever.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:42:23.16,00:42:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>So, I'll just wait, all back-of-the-bus.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:42:27.71,00:42:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>For now.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:42:43.77,00:42:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- How unexpected. \N- An Elemental.
Dialogue: 0,00:42:47.65,00:42:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>- Here? \N- One of the captives.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:42:51.32,00:42:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>And why, after 30 years,</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:42:54.32,00:42:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,should it be you?
Dialogue: 0,00:42:56.78,00:42:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You be the good warrior.
Dialogue: 0,00:42:59.62,00:43:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Go after this Riddick.
Dialogue: 0,00:43:02.58,00:43:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find out why the Lord Marshal \Nis so threatened by him.
Dialogue: 0,00:43:17.97,00:43:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Destination reached.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:43:20.47,00:43:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Unlocking manual controls.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:43:22.47,00:43:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I make 700 degrees \Non the day side,
Dialogue: 0,00:43:24.98,00:43:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,300 below on the night side.
Dialogue: 0,00:43:27.94,00:43:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not get caught in the sun.
Dialogue: 0,00:43:30.98,00:43:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If I owned this place and hell,
Dialogue: 0,00:43:33.48,00:43:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rent this place out \Nand live in hell.
Dialogue: 0,00:43:45.20,00:43:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>- Blue angle... good. \N- Stand by.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:43:49.13,00:43:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>And...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:43:51.17,00:43:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Plotted course good.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:43:53.17,00:43:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit it!
Dialogue: 0,00:43:55.67,00:43:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Angle of approach, not good.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:44:06.85,00:44:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Look, Ma. No hands!</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:44:43.97,00:44:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Party poppers!
Dialogue: 0,00:45:08.33,00:45:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I shit myself.
Dialogue: 0,00:45:11.92,00:45:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Skittish, Toombs. Very skittish.
Dialogue: 0,00:45:36.61,00:45:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Comfy?
Dialogue: 0,00:45:56.00,00:45:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When the ride's over,
Dialogue: 0,00:45:59.46,00:46:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,your goggles are mine.
Dialogue: 0,00:46:30.58,00:46:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Four-way split!
Dialogue: 0,00:46:43.97,00:46:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,29.4 kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,00:46:54.77,00:46:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is Riddick.
Dialogue: 0,00:47:23.76,00:47:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the bowels of Christ \Nare you talkin' about, 700K?
Dialogue: 0,00:47:27.89,00:47:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take this one, boss.
Dialogue: 0,00:47:29.85,00:47:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Anatoli here \Nhas a nose for trouble.
Dialogue: 0,00:47:33.22,00:47:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And this one, this Riddick guy...
Dialogue: 0,00:47:35.64,00:47:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Big, big trouble.
Dialogue: 0,00:47:37.81,00:47:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, 700,000 is good money.
Dialogue: 0,00:47:41.02,00:47:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd take the money, Toombs.
Dialogue: 0,00:47:52.49,00:47:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>The guild pays us a caretaker's fee \Nfor each prisoner each year.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:47:57.08,00:48:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We pay mercs 20% of that total fee \Nbased on a certain life expectancy.
Dialogue: 0,00:48:01.21,00:48:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>How's about this?</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:48:02.92,00:48:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You open that safe you got hidden \Nbehind the console there,
Dialogue: 0,00:48:05.92,00:48:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,show me the real books, \Nthen we figure out my cut.
Dialogue: 0,00:48:10.09,00:48:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll be on my way.
Dialogue: 0,00:48:16.98,00:48:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Open my books. \NThis is what you suggest?
Dialogue: 0,00:48:25.40,00:48:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't a suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,00:48:45.25,00:48:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>These are dangerous days, \Nif you believe the talk.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:48:50.97,00:48:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- Talk? \N- About dead planets.
Dialogue: 0,00:48:54.10,00:48:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,About some ghost army.
Dialogue: 0,00:48:57.31,00:48:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,About them.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:00.02,00:49:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"Them"?
Dialogue: 0,00:49:20.25,00:49:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll run the numbers again.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:22.25,00:49:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes a couple of days, \Nprobably,
Dialogue: 0,00:49:24.42,00:49:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can stay as my guest.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:27.88,00:49:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,At least here, we are all safe.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:29.88,00:49:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>- Yes? \N- Yes, boss.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:49:33.26,00:49:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give it a day.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:38.02,00:49:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,One.
Dialogue: 0,00:50:18.56,00:50:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>There are inmates...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:50:20.56,00:50:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>and there are convicts.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:50:23.39,00:50:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A convict has a certain code.
Dialogue: 0,00:50:26.90,00:50:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And he knows to show \Na certain respect.
Dialogue: 0,00:50:31.90,00:50:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>An inmate, on the other hand,</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:50:34.53,00:50:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,pulls the pin on his fellow man.
Dialogue: 0,00:50:37.12,00:50:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Does the guards' work for them.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:50:39.58,00:50:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Brings shame...
Dialogue: 0,00:50:42.25,00:50:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,To the game.
Dialogue: 0,00:50:46.63,00:50:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So, which are you gonna be?
Dialogue: 0,00:50:49.67,00:50:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,00:50:54.30,00:50:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just passin' through.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:02.43,00:51:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Crematoria.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:25.29,00:51:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They can be quite a test, \Nthese deep runs...
Dialogue: 0,00:51:31.80,00:51:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,tests of our inner selves.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:36.30,00:51:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you find that true?
Dialogue: 0,00:51:42.64,00:51:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Some men do.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:46.06,00:51:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Just being so far from the armada,</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:51:48.65,00:51:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the mind can start to fill \Nwith strange thoughts, doubts.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:54.61,00:51:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you ever have doubts, Vaako?
Dialogue: 0,00:52:00.99,00:52:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- Doubts? \N- About the campaign.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:04.50,00:52:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,About Lord Marshal.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:08.67,00:52:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,First and always, \NI am a Necromonger commander.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:14.09,00:52:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you're here to test my loyalty, \Nyou succeed only in testing my patience.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:19.26,00:52:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. \NNo, that's not why I'm here at all.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:29.06,00:52:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>A young warrior \Nonce consulted a seer.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:52:33.44,00:52:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>He was told a child would be born \Non the planet Furya... a male child...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:52:38.57,00:52:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>who would someday \Ncause the warrior's downfall.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:52:41.78,00:52:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Cause his untimed death.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:52:46.16,00:52:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Furya? Furya's a ruined world. \NNo life to speak of.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:51.21,00:52:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,For good reason.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:52.84,00:52:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This young warrior \Nmounted an attack on Furya,
Dialogue: 0,00:52:57.88,00:53:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,killing all young males \Nhe could find,
Dialogue: 0,00:53:01.05,00:53:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,even strangling some \Nwith their birth cords.
Dialogue: 0,00:53:05.22,00:53:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,An artful stroke, \Nwouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,00:53:09.94,00:53:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So this warrior, the one who tried to \Noutwit the prediction, would later become...
Dialogue: 0,00:53:14.06,00:53:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he worries.
Dialogue: 0,00:53:16.15,00:53:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...our Lord Marshal.
Dialogue: 0,00:53:19.74,00:53:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Which would make \Nthe man-child...
Dialogue: 0,00:53:21.82,00:53:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He worries he missed \Nkilling that child in its crib.
Dialogue: 0,00:53:24.37,00:53:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...Riddick.
Dialogue: 0,00:54:20.26,00:54:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeding time!
Dialogue: 0,00:54:29.93,00:54:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,00:55:35.08,00:55:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaah!
Dialogue: 0,00:57:03.50,00:57:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an animal thing.
Dialogue: 0,00:57:12.30,00:57:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's pop the cork. \NGet some fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,00:57:52.55,00:57:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So they do go topside...
Dialogue: 0,00:57:56.05,00:57:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,to swap out air.
Dialogue: 0,00:57:58.89,00:58:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,00:58:01.39,00:58:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,00:58:05.06,00:58:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,When it happens, it'll happen fast.
Dialogue: 0,00:58:08.53,00:58:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Stay on my leg when I cut fence \Nor stay here...</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:58:12.03,00:58:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,for the rest of your unnatural life.
Dialogue: 0,00:58:14.11,00:58:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody outs this place. \NNobody.
Dialogue: 0,00:58:24.00,00:58:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>He ain't "nobody. "</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:58:40.39,00:58:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Good news first. \NTalked things over with my amigos here.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:58:44.85,00:58:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll cut you in for 775K.
Dialogue: 0,00:58:50.53,00:58:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, all right.
Dialogue: 0,00:58:52.65,00:58:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the bad news? \NThey close the local whorehouse?
Dialogue: 0,00:58:57.70,00:59:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>No. The bad news is worse than that. \NMuch worse.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:59:01.54,00:59:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Our pilot, he saw this. \NIt crossed a shipping lane.
Dialogue: 0,00:59:10.09,00:59:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Any idea what this might be?</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:59:17.22,00:59:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Never saw nothin' like it.
Dialogue: 0,00:59:20.26,00:59:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>This ship charts back \Nto Helion Prime.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:59:24.06,00:59:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Anatoli's \Ngot a nose for trouble,
Dialogue: 0,00:59:27.65,00:59:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>and he thinks \Ntrouble follows you here.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:59:33.82,00:59:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Look. We dusted our tracks \Nand got the hell outta there.</i>
Dialogue: 0,00:59:38.20,00:59:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no way \Nwe didn't lose them.
Dialogue: 0,00:59:42.37,00:59:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"Them"?
Dialogue: 0,00:59:50.71,00:59:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my prisoner. Mine.
Dialogue: 0,00:59:54.01,00:59:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody else's.
Dialogue: 0,00:59:56.09,00:59:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want my money now.
Dialogue: 0,00:59:58.47,01:00:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>So...</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:00:00.64,01:00:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you stole a prisoner...
Dialogue: 0,01:00:03.14,01:00:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,from "them"?
Dialogue: 0,01:01:12.38,01:01:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,01:01:14.67,01:01:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Riddick. No!</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:01:22.97,01:01:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoulda taken the money, Toombs.
Dialogue: 0,01:02:22.90,01:02:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You gonna kill me?
Dialogue: 0,01:02:58.77,01:03:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Mercs.</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:03:02.44,01:03:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Some guards here, \Nbut this can't be all of them.
Dialogue: 0,01:03:06.11,01:03:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Check their slots in the back... \Nand be careful.</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:03:09.49,01:03:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Don't bother.</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:03:11.58,01:03:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Guards ain't there.
Dialogue: 0,01:03:14.04,01:03:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>They figured out the Necros \Nare comin' for me.</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:03:16.83,01:03:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Plan was to clean the bank, \Nghost the mercs,
Dialogue: 0,01:03:20.09,01:03:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,break wide through the tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,01:03:22.09,01:03:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And then somebody got a lucky shot off \Nwith this rocket launcher here...
Dialogue: 0,01:03:25.88,01:03:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and took out the sled.
Dialogue: 0,01:03:27.97,01:03:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Guards took off on foot but rigged \Nthe door so no one could follow.
Dialogue: 0,01:03:33.14,01:03:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>They'll take the one ship in the hangar \Nand leave everyone else here to die.</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:03:37.81,01:03:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How come you know all this shit?
Dialogue: 0,01:03:41.27,01:03:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't even here.
Dialogue: 0,01:03:44.32,01:03:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause it was my plan.
Dialogue: 0,01:03:52.16,01:03:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I shoulda taken the money.
Dialogue: 0,01:04:00.59,01:04:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Riddick!
Dialogue: 0,01:04:14.27,01:04:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>What is this? \NWhat is he thinking?</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:04:17.48,01:04:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>- Once that sun comes up... \N- We'll last five minutes.</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:04:20.48,01:04:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Five minutes. We ain't gonna last \N30 seconds out there.
Dialogue: 0,01:04:24.53,01:04:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll light you up like a match.
Dialogue: 0,01:04:31.12,01:04:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,20-mile buffer zone \Nand 30 klicks to the hangar.
Dialogue: 0,01:04:37.46,01:04:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,30 klicks over that terrain?
Dialogue: 0,01:04:52.35,01:04:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's moving in the right direction. \NWe could make it.
Dialogue: 0,01:04:57.77,01:05:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay behind the night,
Dialogue: 0,01:05:00.52,01:05:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,ahead of the sun.
Dialogue: 0,01:05:02.90,01:05:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's gonna be one speed...
Dialogue: 0,01:05:07.36,01:05:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,mine.
Dialogue: 0,01:05:11.62,01:05:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>If you can't keep up, don't step up.</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:05:13.87,01:05:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll just die.
Dialogue: 0,01:06:19.93,01:06:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Riddick?</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:06:23.77,01:06:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Riddick?
Dialogue: 0,01:06:29.11,01:06:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Riddick?
Dialogue: 0,01:06:35.62,01:06:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, go! Go on! Go! Climb here!
Dialogue: 0,01:06:39.24,01:06:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Climb! Go! Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,01:07:07.61,01:07:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,01:07:13.28,01:07:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Up there.</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:07:15.32,01:07:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- Take a look. \N- Because Anatoli says so?
Dialogue: 0,01:07:17.57,01:07:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Because his nose says so.
Dialogue: 0,01:07:37.97,01:07:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothin' up here.
Dialogue: 0,01:07:42.60,01:07:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,01:07:53.82,01:07:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Riddick.
Dialogue: 0,01:07:56.45,01:08:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>They're heading right for the volcano \Nfields. They're going for our ship!</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:08:00.16,01:08:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No chance do they get to \Nthe hangar first. No chance!
Dialogue: 0,01:08:14.55,01:08:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Next one! Next hole! \NWe'll catch 'em there!
Dialogue: 0,01:08:44.66,01:08:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>No more run for you.</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:08:52.17,01:08:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did the big guy go?
Dialogue: 0,01:09:01.34,01:09:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh...
Dialogue: 0,01:09:28.37,01:09:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Close it!
Dialogue: 0,01:10:01.70,01:10:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that? \NYou don't care if you live or die?
Dialogue: 0,01:10:04.62,01:10:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If I kill them first, not really.
Dialogue: 0,01:10:09.29,01:10:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I do.
Dialogue: 0,01:10:11.46,01:10:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep moving!
Dialogue: 0,01:11:10.77,01:11:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Kyra?</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:11:13.94,01:11:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Get that ass moving!
Dialogue: 0,01:11:57.48,01:11:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"One speed. "
Dialogue: 0,01:12:19.58,01:12:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Temperature differential.
Dialogue: 0,01:12:21.54,01:12:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Your rope.
Dialogue: 0,01:12:23.17,01:12:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late. \NWe're never gonna make it.
Dialogue: 0,01:12:26.55,01:12:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Your rope! Gimme your rope!
Dialogue: 0,01:12:29.76,01:12:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And your water. All of it!
Dialogue: 0,01:12:32.89,01:12:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay in the shadow of the mountain. \NDon't wait for me. Run!
Dialogue: 0,01:12:48.24,01:12:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Riddick!
Dialogue: 0,01:13:01.67,01:13:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaah!
Dialogue: 0,01:13:34.58,01:13:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the hell is that hangar?
Dialogue: 0,01:13:41.50,01:13:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>There it is.</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:13:47.30,01:13:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Listen.</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:14:16.91,01:14:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me guess. Necros.
Dialogue: 0,01:14:44.90,01:14:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I figure we got three minutes before the sun \Nhits us again, burns out this whole valley.
Dialogue: 0,01:14:50.11,01:14:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wait. \N- We gonna do this or not?
Dialogue: 0,01:14:52.90,01:14:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait.
Dialogue: 0,01:15:12.05,01:15:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaah! Boss!
Dialogue: 0,01:15:46.75,01:15:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,On the right!
Dialogue: 0,01:15:55.97,01:15:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out! \NBehind you!
Dialogue: 0,01:15:57.84,01:15:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Kyra!</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:16:55.65,01:16:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sybar!
Dialogue: 0,01:17:59.22,01:18:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>No!</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:19:47.70,01:19:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyra?
Dialogue: 0,01:19:53.79,01:19:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>I was supposed to \Ndeliver a message to you...</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:19:58.71,01:20:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,if Vaako failed to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,01:20:02.88,01:20:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A message from \Nthe Lord Marshal himself.
Dialogue: 0,01:20:07.55,01:20:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He tells you to stay away from Helion, \Nstay away from him,
Dialogue: 0,01:20:12.39,01:20:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and in return, \Nyou'll be hunted no more.
Dialogue: 0,01:20:21.52,01:20:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But Vaako will most likely \Nreport you as dead.
Dialogue: 0,01:20:25.74,01:20:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is your chance.
Dialogue: 0,01:20:27.15,01:20:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Your chance to do \Nwhat no man has ever done.
Dialogue: 0,01:20:31.91,01:20:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl.
Dialogue: 0,01:20:34.95,01:20:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Where will they take her?
Dialogue: 0,01:20:37.87,01:20:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We all began... as something else.
Dialogue: 0,01:20:44.63,01:20:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done... unbelievable things...
Dialogue: 0,01:20:44.76,01:20:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done... unbelievable things...
Dialogue: 0,01:20:48.34,01:20:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,in the name of a faith \Nthat was never my own.
Dialogue: 0,01:20:53.01,01:20:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And he'll do to her \Nwhat he did to me.
Dialogue: 0,01:21:03.23,01:21:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The Necromonger in me \Nwarns you not to go back.
Dialogue: 0,01:21:09.20,01:21:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Furyan in me...
Dialogue: 0,01:21:15.37,01:21:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,hopes you won't listen.
Dialogue: 0,01:22:24.19,01:22:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>I have lost a Purifier...</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:22:28.32,01:22:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>but I have gained \Na first among commanders.</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:22:34.11,01:22:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It is overdue, isn't it...
Dialogue: 0,01:22:36.83,01:22:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that we acknowledge \Nyour many accomplishments,
Dialogue: 0,01:22:39.58,01:22:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>your steady faith,</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:22:41.83,01:22:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and above all, \Nyour unflinching loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,01:22:55.09,01:22:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Obedience without question. \NLoyalty till UnderVerse come.
Dialogue: 0,01:23:01.10,01:23:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Vaako.
Dialogue: 0,01:23:04.35,01:23:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a day of days.
Dialogue: 0,01:23:28.13,01:23:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Now, tell me if it's true.</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:23:30.71,01:23:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me the Furyan is gone, and I can close \Nthis campaign without hearing his bootsteps.
Dialogue: 0,01:23:35.55,01:23:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If he is dead,
Dialogue: 0,01:23:39.64,01:23:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I sense I'm not far \Nfrom the same fate,
Dialogue: 0,01:23:42.73,01:23:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,being of no further use here.
Dialogue: 0,01:23:45.73,01:23:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't I tell you \Nthat Riddick is still alive?
Dialogue: 0,01:23:48.90,01:23:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try me, Aereon.
Dialogue: 0,01:23:50.73,01:23:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I could plough you under \Nwith the rest of Helion Prime.
Dialogue: 0,01:23:53.07,01:23:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No one really knows the future.
Dialogue: 0,01:23:55.49,01:23:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then tell me the odds \Nthat Vaako met with success,
Dialogue: 0,01:23:59.37,01:24:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that I will now be the one...
Dialogue: 0,01:24:01.41,01:24:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,who can carry his people across \Nthe threshold into UnderVerse,
Dialogue: 0,01:24:04.41,01:24:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,where they shall begin true life.
Dialogue: 0,01:24:06.46,01:24:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me what I want to hear, Aereon,
Dialogue: 0,01:24:08.83,01:24:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and maybe \NI'll save your home world... for last.
Dialogue: 0,01:24:17.76,01:24:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- The odds are good... \N
Dialogue: 0,01:24:21.81,01:24:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That Riddick is still alive
Dialogue: 0,01:25:02.43,01:25:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ascension protocol!
Dialogue: 0,01:25:04.31,01:25:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have numbers out there, Lord \NMarshal... sweep teams, recon ships.
Dialogue: 0,01:25:08.10,01:25:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They would be hard-pressed \Nto make it back...
Dialogue: 0,01:25:14.94,01:25:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Get my armada off the ground!
Dialogue: 0,01:26:38.36,01:26:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Final protocol. \NExecute on my order.
Dialogue: 0,01:27:16.81,01:27:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Go inside.
Dialogue: 0,01:28:10.49,01:28:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>We found this Lensor dead.</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:28:15.33,01:28:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Show me his last sight.</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:28:31.18,01:28:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Toal.
Dialogue: 0,01:28:32.93,01:28:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't escape twice.
Dialogue: 0,01:30:27.30,01:30:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay your weapons!
Dialogue: 0,01:30:31.88,01:30:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He came for me.
Dialogue: 0,01:31:00.66,01:31:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Consider this:</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:31:07.88,01:31:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>If you fall here now,</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:31:12.05,01:31:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll never rise.
Dialogue: 0,01:31:14.05,01:31:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>But if you choose another way...</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:31:18.35,01:31:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>the Necromonger way...</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:31:20.60,01:31:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>you'll die in due time...</i>
Dialogue: 0,01:31:23.19,01:31:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and rise again in the UnderVerse.
Dialogue: 0,01:31:36.57,01:31:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to him.
Dialogue: 0,01:31:46.29,01:31:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,01:31:49.29,01:31:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,at first.
Dialogue: 0,01:31:51.63,01:31:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But after a while, the pain \Ngoes away, just as they promise.
Dialogue: 0,01:31:57.64,01:32:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you with me, Kyra? \N- There's a moment...
Dialogue: 0,01:32:00.22,01:32:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,when you can almost \Nsee the UnderVerse through his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,01:32:03.98,01:32:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes it sound perfect...
Dialogue: 0,01:32:06.81,01:32:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,a place where anyone \Ncan start over.
Dialogue: 0,01:32:08.81,01:32:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you with me, Kyra?
Dialogue: 0,01:32:23.83,01:32:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Convert now...
Dialogue: 0,01:32:26.33,01:32:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,or fall forever.
Dialogue: 0,01:32:33.26,01:32:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You killed everything I know.
Dialogue: 0,01:32:40.68,01:32:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Vaako.
Dialogue: 0,01:32:43.97,01:32:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,01:32:57.78,01:33:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Been a long time \Nsince I've seen my own blood.
Dialogue: 0,01:34:19.03,01:34:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,These are his last moments.
Dialogue: 0,01:34:41.63,01:34:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your soul.
Dialogue: 0,01:34:49.52,01:34:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,01:35:58.21,01:36:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not the one to bring me down.
Dialogue: 0,01:36:37.04,01:36:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me, Vaako. Kill him.
Dialogue: 0,01:36:47.72,01:36:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Vaako?
Dialogue: 0,01:36:53.72,01:36:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,01:37:38.85,01:37:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were dead.
Dialogue: 0,01:37:43.69,01:37:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you with me, Kyra?
Dialogue: 0,01:37:48.32,01:37:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I was always with you.
Dialogue: 0,01:37:53.24,01:37:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I was.
Dialogue: 0,01:39:18.91,01:39:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep what you kill.
